        <item>
            <title>广汽首款插电混能旗舰 MPV E9 抵港　续航力长达 1032 公里 + 豪华车箱中排按摩椅</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/26/gac-e9/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gac-e9</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/26/gac-e9/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 02:30:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GAC]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽 E9]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽傅祺]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[纯电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271523</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日（25 日）广汽 GAC 在海港城举办了 E9 插电混能旗舰 MPV 发布会，在满电满油的情况下的极限续航高达 1032 公里，最适合港车北上。新车除了外形时尚，内笼亦非常豪华，加上安全性亦可能属同级车之中最齐，不知能否挑战豪华 MPV 市场的一众日系对手？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_104055-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_104055-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_104055-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>广汽 E9 采用大尺寸家族化格栅设计，搭配 LED 大灯组，突显其现代且豪华的风格。车身侧面线条修长，提供宽敞的内部空间，适合家用及商务接待。车辆的轮圈设计和尾部造型提升了整体的时尚感​。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110548-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110548-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110548-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大尺寸家族化格栅设计</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271548" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110540-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110540-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110540-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LED 大灯组</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110203-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110203-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110203-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>E9 的内笼设计侧重于舒适性，使用高级麂皮和半苯胺真皮座椅，并具备腿托、一键 SPA 和 10 点式按摩功能。无风感空调系统进一步优化了车内的舒适体验，使乘客在旅途中保持放松和舒适。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110223-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110223-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110223-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲高级麂皮和半苯胺真皮座椅</p><p>E9 配备 L2 级别辅助驾驶系统，并具备气囊面积高达 16.3 平方米的 3.2 米 360 度安全气帘及后排气帘，增强车内的安全防护。弹匣电池技术在极端情况下提供高水准的乘客保护，加上全景影像系统，能有效提升驾驶安全性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271547" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110456-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110456-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110456-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲高级麂皮和半苯胺真皮座椅</p><p>广汽 E9 的中控台设计集中于数位化与便捷操作，配备了高清触控萤幕，支持多种娱乐及车内操控功能。萤幕除了显示导航地图、行车资讯和倒车影像外，还支援多媒体播放，让乘客能够在旅程中随时观看影片、播放音乐或使用蓝牙连接功能，连接手机免提通话和播放音乐。此外，中控台还具备无线充电板，方便乘客无需额外充电线即可为手机进行充电，提升车内的便利性和舒适性​</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110355-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110355-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110355-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110306-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110306-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110306-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中控台高清触控萤幕</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110447-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110447-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110447-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲具备无线充电板</p><p>E9 的全液晶仪表板则进一步强化了行车资讯的可视化，能够即时显示车速、油量、电量、导航提示及驾驶辅助系统状态等资讯。此仪表板采用直观易读的界面设计，让驾驶者在行驶中能快速查看所需资讯，从而提升对车辆状态的掌控，减少视线偏离的时间，进一步提升了驾驶安全性</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110304-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110304-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110304-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">在动力系统方面，E9 配备 2.0T 引擎与双挡 DHT 变速箱，形成智电插混系统。此系统在城市短途出行时可使用纯电模式，长途驾驶时切换至混合动力模式，达到 1000 公里以上的续航。E9 还具备 220V 外放电功能，支持户外用电​。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110315-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110315-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110315-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>广汽 E9 的车内设计考虑到了灵活空间的需求，其行李厢最大容积可达 1500L，能够轻松应对大量行李或多样化的储物需求，特别适合长途旅行或多人出行时使用。此外，车内设计了多处储物空间，包括 15 处挂钩、15 处储物盒和 14 处杯托，确保乘客的物品能妥善安置，进一步增强了车内的实用性与便利性​。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110432-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110432-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025_110432-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲容量可达 1500L</p><h2>规格</h2><table><tbody><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="height: 48px;">长 x 宽 x 高 (mm)</td><td style="height: 48px;">5212 x 1893 x 1823</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="height: 24px;">轴距 (mm)</td><td style="height: 24px;">3070</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="height: 24px;">最大马力 (Ps)</td><td style="height: 24px;">190</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="height: 24px;">最大功率 (kW/rpm)</td><td style="height: 24px;">140</td></tr><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="height: 48px;">最大扭矩 (N·m/rpm)</td><td style="height: 48px;">330</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="height: 24px;">油箱容量 (L)</td><td style="height: 24px;">56</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="height: 24px;">座位数</td><td style="height: 24px;">7</td></tr><tr><td>续航</td><td><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 50%;">纯电</td><td style="width: 50%;"> 106 km（WLTC）</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">混合动力模式</td><td style="width: 50%;">1032 km</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><h2>售价：</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 14.1447%;">顶配版：</td><td style="width: 85.8553%;">港币 628,000 元<br />
（首 100 辆可享早鸟优惠，早鸟价为港币 599,000 元）</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 14.1447%;">中配版：</td><td style="width: 85.8553%;">港币 558,000 元</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/27/nissan-ariya/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Nissan ARIYA 纯电动旗舰 SUV 抵港　首创 e-4ORCE 电子四驱 + 594 公里特长续航</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/13/korea-electric-car-chargered-90more-cannot-enter-basement-carpark/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">韩禁电量逾 90％ 电动车驶入地下停车场，避免电动车发生火警</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/11/new-smart-5-set-for-august-28-reveal-date/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Smart #5 纯电 SUV 8 月 28 登场　越野实力全面提升 + 史上最大部 Smart</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/26/gac-e9/life-tech/auto/">广汽首款插电混能旗舰 MPV E9 抵港　续航力长达 1032 公里 + 豪华车箱中排按摩椅</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
